+files bearing 2.19x/2.22x/2.26x carry retirement/supersession framing (including `drafts/paper.md:540-566`,
+`drafts/paper.es.md:591-610`, `docs/101_CORE_V0_MINIMAL_PUBLISHABLE_MODEL.md:5-12`,
